        <h2>Diet Plan</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Breakfast:</strong> Scrambled eggs with avocado toast and a fruit smoothie.</li>
            <li><strong>Lunch:</strong> Grilled chicken with quinoa and steamed vegetables.</li>
            <li><strong>Snacks:</strong> Nuts, dried fruits, and a protein shake.</li>
            <li><strong>Dinner:</strong> Baked salmon with sweet potatoes and sautéed spinach.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Gym Routine</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Strength training (compound lifts) 4 times a week.</li>
            <li>Low-intensity cardio (walking, cycling) 2 times a week.</li>
            <li>Core and flexibility workouts (planks, stretching) daily.</li>
        </ul>
